#. Tag: para
#: libvirt_configuration.xml:1631
#, no-c-format
msgid "<replaceable>GUEST</replaceable> needs to be replaced by the domain name, id or uuid of the &vmguest; and -- <replaceable>OPTION</replaceable> can be one of the following:"
